Maintainer: Joshua Marie Ongcoy <joshuaongcoy26@gmail.com>
Description: A composable grammar for building Monte Carlo simulations, 
    inspired by the grammar-of-graphics and tidyverse semantics design. 
    The package allows for stepwise declarations of random variables, 
    deterministic transformations, replication, collection, and analysis 
    of simulated data. It supports reproducibility and HPC-aware design.
